NOTE ON THE BREAK VIDEO

This MIT license covers the source code only. The optional break video
(Resources/productivity_break.mp4) is NOT part of this repository and is NOT
distributed with it — it is third-party artwork that Scripts/fetch-video.sh can
download for your personal use. You are responsible for ensuring you have the
right to use any video you supply via that script or the
PRODUCTIVITY_BREAK_VIDEO environment variable. The built-in default animal is
drawn in code and is covered by this license.
